Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.11,0:10:44.28,ED2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\an8}あの雲の彼方へ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.51,0:10:48.66,ED2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\an8}私をつれていって
